@jburnmurdoch Fascinating that South Africa 🇿🇦 is below its baseline death rate, during #COVID19. Lockdown presumably reduced murder as well as road deaths? Easter weekend road deaths down to 28 this yr, versus 126 & 309 in prior 2 years.  ER docs, what are you seeing?

https://t.co/4pkSKXbYmK
